videos.description: Jeff Roberson lines up and knocks down a long 3-pointer to make it a one-point game.
videos.headline: Roberson hits long 3 for Vandy

videos.description: Kevin Knox misses a 3-pointer but follows up with a finger-roll layup.
videos.headline: Knox collects his rebound for finger-roll

videos.description: Joe Toye cuts along the baseline and draws the foul on the reverse for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Toye hits reverse up and under and-1

videos.description: Riley LaChance caps off a 10-0 run for the Commodores with a 3-pointer to go up 29-23.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's LaChance knocks down open 3

videos.description: Vanderbilt's head coach Bryce Drew says his under-sized team has to get tough if they want to keep their lead over Kentucky in the second half.
videos.headline: Drew: 'We have to be relentless'

videos.description: Ejike Obinna rolls off the screen and draws the foul on the dunk from Nick Richards for the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Obinna dunks for and-1

videos.description: Kentucky's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander hits a jumper falling down as he draws the foul to cut the Wildcats' deficit to 7.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander hits and-1 jumper

videos.description: Kevin Knox makes it a 4-point game with a 3-pointer to cut into the Commodores lead.
videos.headline: Knox cuts deficit with 3 ball

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander cuts Vanderbilt's lead to one with a drive inside and a left-hand finish for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander drives in for a finger-roll

videos.description: Clevon Brown denies Quade Green at the rim sparking a hectic sequence finished with a layup by Joe Toye to put Vanderbilt up 70-65.
videos.headline: Brown block leads to late Vandy layup

videos.description: Kentucky's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander goes up strong to score his 30th point as the Wildcats score early in overtime.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander scores first in OT

videos.description: Payton Willis knocks down a 3-pointer in overtime to make it a one-point game, followed quickly by a 3-pointer from Kevin Knox.
videos.headline: Willis hits 3 for Vandy, Knox responds

videos.description: Kevin Knox drives and pulls up to draw the foul giving the Wildcats a one-point lead late in overtime.
videos.headline: Knox goes up strong for OT and-1

videos.description: Quade Green cuts through the Vanderbilt defense with seconds left in overtime to give Kentucky an 83-81 win.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Green drives for OT winner

videos.description: Kentucky head coach John Calipari says Vanderbilt did everything they were supposed to do to win and that his team still has a lot to learn.
videos.headline: Calipari: 'I don't know how we won this game'

videos.description: Kentucky's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander says his team needs to learn to fight for a full game after another tight comeback win.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander: 'We need to fight a full 40'
